"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rHAR6xK6DuJVH8XLmRDx_.png?height=1080&width=1920)\\n\\n**Hello Ninjas! Happy new year to all of youü•∑**\\n\\nWe hope you had a great time with your loved ones and that you‚Äôre anticipating 2022 just as we do.‚ù§Ô∏è\\n\\n2021 marks the start of NinjaDAOs and we‚Äôre more than thankful for your continued support. Last year we focused on bringing our ideas forward and having a successful launch on web and IOS.\\n\\nThis year will kick off our steps into the P2E universe with more possibilities and we‚Äôre more than excited for this.\\n\\nWe would love to announce the latest updates on NinjaDAOs:\\n\\n### Bind your Discord\\n\\n1. For any new Ninjas signing up, you will be directed to link your Discord account.\\n2. For exisiting Ninjas, you can click your profile pic to choose \\\"Bind your Discord\\\".\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/woGrQcDLvTN14L5pQUubU.png?height=1422&width=2872)\\n\\n### Private channel\\n\\n1. To smooth communication between managers and scholars, Ninjas can now join private channels when a scholarship comes into effect (you will need to join NinjaDAOs server and bind your discord first).\\n\\n### Rename your scholarship anytime\\n\\n1. Ninjas are now free to rename any scholarship at any point.\\n\\n### Related Links\\n\\nFollow our Twitter:¬†<https://twitter.com/NinjaDAOs>\\n\\nJoin our Discord:¬†<https://discord.gg/Kpsk9tWXS4>\\n\\nVisit our Website:¬†[app.ninjadaos.com](https://app.ninjadaos.com/)\\n\\nRead our Docs:¬†[https://ninjadaos.notion.site/NinjaDAOs-WiKi-e6709296d97445b988a3bb87b552e3f9](https://www.notion.so/NinjaDAOs-WiKi-e6709296d97445b988a3bb87b552e3f9)\",\"timestamp\":1641542392,\"title\":\"NinjaDAOs community update #4\"},\"digest\":\"MoHEJmgwk9j2BmkbpxPB5eRmQ9w7_Cd8Njx9QV8WOVg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc0036DE26673B6E6F404Fd1B32c6735b4Ca8FF43\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,